    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-quality condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! It's been pampered since day one and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless, you\u2019ve found it! Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
