    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-standard condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and free of aesthetic or mechanical imperfections, it offers an uncompromising experience for the most discerning driver. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. We invite you to inspect this singular example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 44500.0,
