    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with this absolute beauty, and let me tell you, she is in pristine, showroom condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014spotless interior, gleaming paint, and it drives like a total dream. It honestly feels brand new! I\u2019m looking for a quick sale, so come grab this gem before someone else does. You really have to see it in person to believe how perfect it is!",
