    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in museum-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-variable differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced and the rod bearing service is fully documented, mitigating common platform vulnerabilities. The suspension geometry remains true with original bushings and dampers, maintaining the factory-intended kinematic balance. Finished in flawless Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the interior shows zero bolster wear or electronic pixel degradation. A mechanically synchronized, turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
